Extract files from ESR BI reporting tool:

Open ESR Business Intelligent Reporting 
Catalog - select NHS Staff List in MY FOLDER area

Open NHS Staff List and change criteria for the latest reporting year (i.e. 31/03/2024).


ESR BI Report parameters

Snapshot Date – End of previous financial year (Prompt will default to this date for each year)
Gender – Select Male and Female
Payroll – 914 Monthly BSA (Eliminates Hosted staff not required for report)
Employee Person Type – Employee

All other parameters can be left as is.


Sometimes, new pay_scale appears and it makes afc_band NA. in that case, you will need to update directorate_lookup.csv file or afc_band_lookup.csv file.
